data.description: Beautiful Cape Cod style 1.5 Story on level lot. As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by its inviting facade, featuring a covered porch perfect for sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a beautiful sunset. Step inside to discover an open and spacious floor plan, with a cozy living room. The adjacent kitchen offers ample cabinet space and a center island, providing an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. The primary suite includes a full bath and walk in closet. Upstairs you will find two spacious bedrooms and a full bath. Don't miss the 3 car detached garage with it's own furnace and AC. Only minutes from the marina, boat ramp, pool, club house, beach and lake access points.   Beaver Lake offers 320 acres of water to ski, fish, swim, boat, jet ski and enjoy. AMA.
